Alusuisse of America Inc. plan to sell Consolidated Aluminum Corp. subsidiary as part of im strategy to put more attention to di aluminium packaging wey dey U.S.

Alusuisse, for New York, no talk how much e dey expect for unit, di company don employ First Boston Corp to help identify bidder.

Alusuisse na subsidiary of Swiss Aluminium Ltd, Zurich, Switzerland, wey be sey dey produce aluminium, chemicals, and package product.

Di konsolidated wey get 1988 revenue of $400 million, na im dey sell aluminium sheet, aluminium foil for Hannibal, Ohio, Jackson, tentn, rolling mills, and recycle aluminium for one plant for Bens Run, W.Va.

